  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, I donated portion of the money for the poor, which you had with you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember those words very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So then he said, what we need now is, you have to be seen by a doctor.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was seen by a doctor, who was trying to tell what not to do, what to do, and so on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And no matter how I was trying to follow instructions, not to eat a lot suddenly and so on, I suddenly gained too much weight.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very blown up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the skin on my body, which was shriveled, especially in joints like my knee and my elbow, stretched out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was kind of watery under the freshly stretched-out skin and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I gained back strength slowly and so on, and life begun, the free life begun.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were always very respectful of the Russians on the street, where the Russian occupying force was present in Budapest, because they were catching everybody and anybody.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I said that, catching everybody and anybody, I have to come back to an incident on my walk from Harka, on the road after-- before-- before I experienced getting this transportation which I was talking about.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was a portion I was across with a bunch of bicycles, which were left on the roadside.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had a love for bicycles as a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was a 16-year-old, 15-year-old, very much involved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when I could go to the stadium at age 14-- and later on, you couldn't enter the stadium and so on-- I was part of a team for a bicycle race group who were assembling bicycles and changing wheels and so forth.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
